@startuml architecture
' Schéma d'architecture 3-tiers (Figure 10 du rapport)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #EFF6FF
  BorderColor #2563EB
  FontName "Helvetica"
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #DCFCE7
  BorderColor #16A34A
  FontName "Helvetica"
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor #FEF3C7
  BorderColor #D97706
}
skinparam ArrowColor #1E293B

actor "Administrateur\nCA TIC" as Admin

cloud "Navigateur" as Browser

frame "Docker Compose — réseau app-network" {
  rectangle "Frontend\nNginx + build Vite\n:8081" as Front #EFF6FF
  rectangle "Backend\nNode.js 22 + Express.js\n+ LibreOffice (carbone)\n:3000" as Back #EFF6FF
  database "MariaDB 10\n:3306" as DB #DCFCE7
  rectangle "Backup\nAlpine + mariadb-client\n+ crond (hebdo)" as Bk #FEF3C7
  rectangle "Volumes\n• mariadb_data (named)\n• backend/uploads (bind)\n• backup/data (bind)" as Vols #F8FAFC
}

Admin -down-> Browser : Saisie / clics
Browser -down-> Front : HTTP / static files\n(SPA Vue.js bundle)
Browser -right-> Back : XHR /api/*\n(proxifié par Nginx)
Front .right.> Back : proxy /api/*\n(vhost Nginx)
Back -down-> DB : SQL\n(driver mariadb-node, pool 5)
Back -right-> Vols : R/W documents,\ntemplate certificat
Bk -down-> DB : mariadb-dump\n(0 6 * * 1)
Bk -right-> Vols : dumps SQL\nbackup_<date>.sql

note bottom of Back
  Pattern Routes → Controller →
  Service → Model.
  Helpers : withConnection(fn),
  validation env vars au boot,
  promisify(carbone.render).
end note

note right of DB
  6 tables :
  person, internship,
  activity, category,
  internship_activity (CASCADE),
  activity_category (RESTRICT)
end note

@enduml
